  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Explorative comparison of montelukast with inhaled steroids (fluticasone) to estimate
      responder profiles, in terms of symptom scores, rescue medication, increase of FEV1, in
      correlation to presence of allergy, bronchial hyperreactivity (PD20), exhaled NO, excretion
      of leukotrienes, response to RABA and laboratory parameters in patients with pre-school
      asthma i.e. asthma phenotypes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
